message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper discusses a deep learning framework for lung cancer diagnosis using 3D lung CAT scans, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also focuses on medical imaging and diagnosis, which could fall under the medical imaging (cs.MED) sub-category. Finally, the use of deep learning models for diagnosis could also fall under the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NEURON) sub-category.
